# ── GitLearn Environment Variables ─────────────────────────────────────────────

# GitHub Personal Access Token
# Increases API rate limit from 60 → 5,000 requests/hr (strongly recommended)
# Generate at: https://github.com/settings/tokens  (no scopes needed for public repos)
GITHUB_TOKEN=your_github_token_here

# Anthropic API Key — OPTIONAL
# If absent, Learn/Quiz/Practice pages use built-in sample content instead of AI.
# Get a key at: https://console.anthropic.com
ANTHROPIC_API_KEY=your_anthropic_key_here
